high_descs: Step slight to the right and then  go forward to the sink.
Pick up the pink soap from the sink counter top.
Go slightly to the left and go to the sink.
Place the bar of soap in the sink and wet the bar. Turn off the water and take out the soap.
Turn to the left and then left again to face the bath tub.
Place the bar of soap in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Wet a bar of soap and move it to the bath tub.

high_descs: Walk slightly to the left and turn right towards the bar of soap on the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Walk slightly to the left to the sink and turn right to face it.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn left and walk to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap in the bath tub basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned bar of soap in a bath tub.

high_descs: Go to the counter between the two sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap from the counter.
Go to the sink to your left.
Clean the bar of soap in the sink.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right to go to the tub.
Put the bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the tub.
